  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  HIV-infected ART-naive subjects with &lt;350 CD4 T cells/mm3 or AIDS

          -  Initiating ART with any first-line regimen recommended in the Spanish GESIDA National
             Guidelines

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt;18 years

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Type 1 or 2 diabetes

          -  End-stage renal disease

          -  Lactose intolerance

          -  Use of immunomodulatory drugs

          -  Neutrophil count &lt;750cells/uL
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
